      <p class="section-intro fade-in">The current Word experience includes an in-canvas prompt bar, a Copilot side pane, contextual rewrite tools, attachment options, agents, model selection, and voice input. Feature availability can vary by license, tenant policy, app version, and service capacity.</p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">📄</div>
          <h3>Draft with Copilot</h3>
