        </article>
        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">💬</div>
          <h3>Copilot side pane</h3>
          <p>Use the side pane to ask questions, edit the document, attach content, select agents, choose models, and continue conversations.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">🧩</div>
          <h3>Selected-text tools</h3>
          <p>Highlight text to rewrite, refine, shorten, expand, adjust tone, or transform notes into a table.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">📎</div>
          <h3>Grounding and files</h3>
          <p>Add work content, upload files, or attach cloud files so Copilot can use the right source material.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-icon">🤖</div>
          <h3>Agents</h3>
          <p>Use approved agents like Researcher, Analyst, Legal Agent, or domain-specific assistants for specialized work.</p>
