  <section id="checklist">
    <div class="cgw-container">
      <p class="cgw-section-label fade-in">Readiness</p>
      <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Success checklist</h2>
      <p class="section-intro fade-in">Use this as a completion gate before learners consider a Copilot-assisted document ready to share.</p>
      <div class="checklist-panel fade-in">
        <div class="progress-label"><span id="progress-count">0</span> of 10 complete</div>
        <div class="progress-bar-wrapper"><div class="progress-bar" id="progress-bar"></div></div>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li class="checklist-item" data-check="0" onclick="toggleCheck(this)"><span class="checklist-checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false"></span><span><span class="checklist-title">Goal is clear</span><span class="checklist-desc">The user knows what output Copilot should produce.</span></span></li>
          <li class="checklist-item" data-check="1" onclick="toggleCheck(this)"><span class="checklist-checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false"></span><span><span class="checklist-title">Right mode selected</span><span class="checklist-desc">Allow editing or Chat only was chosen intentionally.</span></span></li>
          <li class="checklist-item" data-check="2" onclick="toggleCheck(this)"><span class="checklist-checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false"></span><span><span class="checklist-title">Sources are appropriate</span><span class="checklist-desc">Files and work content are approved for the task.</span></span></li>
          <li class="checklist-item" data-check="3" onclick="toggleCheck(this)"><span class="checklist-checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false"></span><span><span class="checklist-title">Prompt has context</span><span class="checklist-desc">Audience, situation, tone, and format are defined.</span></span></li>
          <li class="checklist-item" data-check="4" onclick="toggleCheck(this)"><span class="checklist-checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false"></span><span><span class="checklist-title">Assumptions are labeled</span><span class="checklist-desc">Unsupported claims are flagged, not hidden.</span></span></li>
          <li class="checklist-item" data-check="5" onclick="toggleCheck(this)"><span class="checklist-checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false"></span><span><span class="checklist-title">Facts are verified</span><span class="checklist-desc">Names, numbers, citations, and dates were checked.</span></span></li>
          <li class="checklist-item" data-check="6" onclick="toggleCheck(this)"><span class="checklist-checkbox" role="checkbox" aria-checked="false"></span><span><span class="checklist-title">Sensitive data reviewed</span><span class="checklist-desc">No over-sharing or unapproved sensitive content.</span></span></li>
